  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "落ちてくるバーに合わせて、適切なタイミングで正しいボタンを押すお馴染みの音楽アクション。ゲームには、誰もが知っているメジャーな曲を中心に、20曲以上が収録されています。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Beatmania GB Gotcha Mix 2 is a videogame launched for Game Boy Color. It has 25 songs and it's the last portable videogame for beatmania franchise, and it's the only one from the trilogy to have \"Duet\" charts, which two players are needed to play this level via Game Boy link cable, two GBC's, and two copies of the same game.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
